{"tid":268852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「Gel頭」賊偷女人底褲 阿妹：望住都照偷","createTime":"2017-06-03T10:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T11:02:46.000Z","uid":3066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5220b0da050f3d6d43f9fef88f92846794bbe6a","tid":268852,"uid":3066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:23:17.000Z","msg":"【16：52更新】新增動新聞<br />\n長沙灣青山道249號一唐樓劏房，中午12時許，姓黃（29歲）女住客在屋內見到一名青年，在隔鄰大廈的天台徘徊，未幾見青年伸手掹走一條掛在其窗外的內褲，她喝止不果，賊人沿樓梯飛奔逃走，黃婦大驚報警求助，警員在附近兜截未有發現疑人，並提醒女住客將內衣褲掛回屋內。<br />\n<br />\n據女事主胞妹表示，她姐姐一家五口住上址，包括丈夫、家姑及兩子女。今日黃妹到來探訪姐姐，在廚房見到一名年約20至30歲的青年，在隔鄰247號唐樓天台徘徊，她告知胞姐，事主甫望出天台，即見該名青年伸手掹走掛在窗外冷氣機底部的一條內褲，然後拔足狂奔，過程僅一分鐘。黃婦報警求助。<br />\n黃妹稱，其姐曾向她表示，過往已被人偷內褲至少3、4次，「次次唔同人㗎！有啲賊年紀較大，唔係今次咁後生」，其姐姐家姑的內褲亦曾被偷。事實上天台尚有其他內衣褲掛在晾衣繩上，唯賊人卻偏要伸手掹走掛得較高的內褲，叵心難測，該名賊人年約20至30歲，gel頭，穿白衫短褲。"},{"pid":"8b3ee8ae51c187629dc653437e20fc02d20c15db","tid":268852,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"報導來源 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170603/56778087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170603%2F56778087&d=soNRc1toP2VYVWC%2FYI%2BOFDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=3edc23a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170603%2F56778087&h=53b2a640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170603/56778087</a>"},{"pid":"216228a4f2c4793621ba8465a4b11f5206e0afe9","tid":268852,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/182430_eaf1e81188264fa00d300ca30c879e80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F182430_eaf1e81188264fa00d300ca30c879e80.jpg&h=60bf3565&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ab49a6be2dc996afdadf37c1ea22db0f330c6dc","tid":268852,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:26:21.000Z","msg":"索d黃甘甘既尿漬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b054b774ca46566479cceefa9a1db8ba0eeb6c50","tid":268852,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:30:18.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打等錢洗 諗住偷黎賣二手底底？"},{"pid":"2addbf8a93394952b1aae864e6531fcf217bd920","tid":268852,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:31:19.000Z","msg":"點知偷錯家姑果條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc13b7926688ee0c0006d2a2dab91b6988018483","tid":268852,"uid":108685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點知偷錯家姑果條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n家姑心境年輕 專著花邊底褲 今次條友真係中撚晒伏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7af0209c61d992b2b45c5b4b460bef8a983feeb","tid":268852,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"好重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1841e656b88d78fe81c5ea98241227b405d14300","tid":268852,"uid":619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:37:27.000Z","msg":"29歲就俾人叫黃婦咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d0424bf52fe48a3d4a930c798e734057b6a78a","tid":268852,"uid":72227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"20-30歲 (gel頭)"},{"pid":"36753886037d189c138f1756746c84b0df1bb8a1","tid":268852,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40878e1b31444e34d9dd9e710645d9d868e58cc6","tid":268852,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:02:46.000Z","msg":"「次次唔同人㗎！有啲賊年紀較大，唔係今次咁後生」"}]}